This is a torrent upload script! :)

to get this: 
git clone git://github.com/NChief/nb-upload.git
git checkout rt-relay

place .nb-upload.cfg in your home directory and edit it to fit you!

This is for use with rTorrent. to automaticly upload torrent downloaded based on watch folder.

add this to .rtorrent.rc:
# Start rt-relay
# watch dir with custom3 set.
schedule = watch_directory_1,10,10,"load_start=/home/user/torrents/nbul/*.torrent,d.set_directory=/home/user/Uploads/,d.set_custom3=NBUL"

# On finnished, run script.
system.method.set_key = event.download.finished,upload_me,"execute=screen,-dmS,rtscripts,~/scripts/rtorrent/nb-upload.pl,\"$d.get_loaded_file=\",\"$d.get_base_path=\",$d.get_custom3=,&"
# END

edit it to fit you.
